  m_text: Due to frequent shifts in religion, it is culturally difficult to create
    an effective boogeyman for children. This is <color=#FF00AA><b>Akry</b></color>,
    a creature made of excuses and dust bunnies, a secular boogeyman that passes
    down through the administrations.
